org.lsmp.djep.xjep
Class TreeUtils

java.lang.Object
  org.lsmp.djep.xjep.TreeUtils

public class TreeUtils
extends java.lang.Object

A set of Utility functions for working with JEP expression trees. Main methods are

  • isConstant test if its a constant. Many other is... methods.
  • getValue extracts the value from a node without needing to cast and check types.

Author:
rich
